# ============================================================================
# JOURNAL BACKUP - APPWRITE CLOUD
# ============================================================================
# Steps:
#   1. Go to https://cloud.appwrite.io → Sign up (GitHub login)
#   2. Create project: "journal-backup"
#   3. Go to Databases → Create database: "journal-db"
#   4. Create collection: "entries" with attributes:
#      - t (String, optional, size 200)
#      - d (String, optional, size 2000)
#      - w (String, optional, size 500)
#      - g (String, optional, size 500)
#      - h (String, optional, size 500)
#      - m (Integer, optional, min 0, max 5)
#      - ts (String, required, size 30)
